Has anyone ever seen a T205 Jake Daubert card with any of the following backs:

American Beauty Black or Green, 
Broad Leaf Black or Green, 
Cycle, 
Drum, 
Hassan Factory 30 or 649, 
Hindu, 
Piedmont Factory “42” 

Were T205 Dauberts with these backs ever made?

If someone happens to have one, I would love to know it exists or see it.  Better yet, if you would be willing to part with it, please let me know. 

I have the other more common ones (Piedmont Factory 25, Polar Bear, Sovereign, Honest Long Cut, Sweet Caporal 25 Black and Red, Sweet Caporal 42 Black).  They are part of my on-going Daubert Master Set so they are not for sale.  I'm just wondering whether I should keep looking for the ones I don't have.  Thanks.

Steve,
I believe you are done.  The others do not exist.  Congrats.
